      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "(e) The objects sighted have been described as follows:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "(1) To Lt. [REDACTED] it appeared as two orange lights",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "rotating about a common center. \"like two jet aircraft making slow",
      "status": "correction_required"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "rolls in tight formation\". It had a wide speed range.",
      "status": "correction_required"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "(2) To [REDACTED] and [REDACTED], it appeared as a reddish",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "sphere ball of fire about one foot in diameter, travelling at a high",
      "status": "correction_required"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "rate of speed.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "(3) To Lt. [REDACTED], AD1, it appeared to",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "be a pulsating orange yellow projectile shaped flame, with regular period",
      "status": "correction_required"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "of pulsation on 3 to 5 seconds, off 3 to 5 seconds. Later, as the object",
      "status": "correction_required"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "increased the range the pulsation appeared to increase to on 7 to 8",
      "status": "correction_required"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "seconds and off 7 to 8 seconds.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "3. A check with the Navy Weather Central, Kodiak, Alaska revealed that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "balloons were released at the following times:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "22 January -- 0445 and 2000 (approximately)",
      "status": "correction_required"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "23 January -- 0400 (approximately)",
      "status": "correction_required"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "4. On 23 January winds aloft at 1000 feet were reported at 0400M as",
      "status": "correction_required"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "from 310° T at 36 knots, and at 2000 feet from 240° T at 37 knots, while",
      "status": "correction_required"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "the object was reported to be on an ascending - westerly course.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "5. In view of the fact that no weather balloons were known to have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "been released within a reasonable time before the sightings, it",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "appears that the object or objects were not balloons. If not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "balloons the objects must be regarded as phenomena (possibly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "meteorites), the exact nature of which could not be determined",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "by this office.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
